reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy Pencil Pouch
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this case because a friend of mine had one and I liked the size and style of it. I have enjoyed this pencil pouch for about a year and it has held up great. The light green color is beautiful and I like the metal zipper tab. I appreciate the two inside mesh pockets and the internal zipper pocket. I would recommend this product!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These pencil bags are perfect for holding an asthma inhaler and a spacer. We use them for making all our asthma kits. They are easy for children to open and close and the spacer fits inside easily. There is an internal pocket that can hold some antihistamine tablets and an Apple AirTag (if you are like me and like to track your asthma kits). The bags are discrete enough for your child who is probably reaching the self-carry age right around the same time they become very self-conscious about carrying a bag that screams medical supplies.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy Canvas Pencil Case & Makeup Organizer—A 5-Star Essential!
reviews.reviewText: This canvas pencil case is a game-changer! It doubles as a practical and durable makeup organizer, earning a solid 5-star rating. Here's why I love it:1. Built to last: The sturdy canvas material ensures long-lasting durability for daily use.2. Versatile design: It effortlessly holds pencils, pens, supplies, makeup essentials, cables etc. with multiple side compartments and for organized storage.3. Convenient size: Perfect for both home and travel, fitting easily into bags or backpacks. Opens wide and stays open allowing you to find what you need quickly and easily!4. Easy to clean: Wipe clean with a damp cloth—spills and stains vanish effortlessly.5. Secure closure: The nice zipper keeps everything safely in place, preventing any accidental spills or losses.In summary, this canvas pencil case is a must-have for artists and makeup lovers alike. I have two! Its durability, versatility, and easy maintenance make it an exceptional choice.
